  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nWhen constructing WritableStreams, UnderlyingSinkBase can be exposed  \nby setting getter for \"type\" [ref-wr], and UnderlyingSinkBase::start  \naccepts arbitrary v8 value as argument, which is converted to  \nWritableStreamDefaultController without type checks [ref-vuln]."
